title: #92Noon! Russo in for PA! Custance/Guerin/Krawczynski/Dubnyk/Gleeman & Hayes/LaPanta
description: Michael Russo is in for PA, and he's joined by the illustrious line up of Craig Custance, editor and chief of The Athletic, as well as GM of the Minnesota Wild, Bill Guerin. Checking with Jonny Athletic himself, and goaltender for the Wild, Devan Dubnyk. Then it's a Twins round table with elite baseball minds, Aaron Gleeman & Dan Hayes. And finally, Russo's nemesis, Fox Sports' Anthony LaPanta.
